== webkitgtk-android API - Package Overview ==

GTK 4 widget embedding Android System WebView (WebKitGTK-shaped subset).

Public namespace:

 * ''WebKitGtkAndroid'' — ''WebView'', cookies, downloads, network session

Host a11y entry points (''wka_host_a11y_*'') live in the checked-in VAPI /
host header — not as methods on ''WebView'' (same split as webview2-gtk).

Hand-written notes: [[../a11y.md|docs/a11y.md]], [[../android-build.md|docs/android-build.md]].
